                               <span class="type">Raw</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/us_data/StateIndexRaw.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/us_data/StateIndexRaw.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </article>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class="data_set clearfix">\r\n                            <header>\r\n                                <h2 id="world_data_sets">World Data Sets</h2>\r\n                            </header>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Standard">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Standard</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexStandard.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexStandard.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Chain-Linked">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Chain-Linked</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexChained.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexChained.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Raw">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Raw</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexRaw.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/world_data/WorldIndexRaw.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </article>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </section>\r\n\r\n                <a name="using-the-api"></a>\r\n                    <section class="post box post-349 standard_post gray-box large-6 medium-6 columns">\r\n                        <div class="border row clearfix">\r\n                            <div class="content">\r\n                                <header>\r\n                                    <h2>Using The API</h2>\r\n                                    <hr>\r\n                                </header>\r\n                                <article>\r\n                                    <p>The Quality of Life Measures provides a REST-ful API to allow for the downloading of custom selections based on the completed dataset. Using the API, you can download a subset of countries, years, and indicators, as well as recalculate dimension and summary scores from that subset.</p>\r\n                                    <p>The API returns data in the JSON format.</p>\r\n                                    <a class="btn flat blue " href="<?php echo home_url(); ?>/api-registration">Register for the API</a>\r\n                                </article>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </section>\r\n                    <a name="the-report"></a>\r\n                    <section class="post box post-364 standard_post gray-box large-6 medium-6 columns">\r\n                        <div class="border row clearfix">\r\n                            <div class="content">\r\n                                <header>\r\n                                    <h2>The Report</h2>\r\n                                    <hr>\r\n                                </header>\r\n                                <article>\r\n                                    <p>The 2014 Measures of Quality of Life present an innovative and comprehensive picture of Quality of Life Measures throughout the world and across the 50 U.S. States.</p>\r\n                                    <p>This inaugural report lays out these new measures, with comprehensive scores and rankings covering more than 10 years and more than 40 variables.</p>\r\n                                    <a class="btn flat blue download pdf" href ="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/pdf/Well-Being_Report_Book.pdf" target="_blank" style="background-image: url(&#39;<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/icons/pdf.png&#39;);">Download the Report</a>\r\n                                </article>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </section>\r\n                    <a name="explore-the-map"></a>\r\n                    <section class="post box post-365 standard_post  large-6 medium-6 columns">\r\n                        <div class="border row clearfix">\r\n                            <div class="content">\r\n                                <img src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/cki-template12-getdata-img.j