n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <p></p>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <p></p>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td>years</td>\r\n                                <td>\r\n                                    Returns all of the data for the individual years passed in on the request. Also compares the state scores of the returned years and ranks those states accordingly.\r\n                                    <p></p>\r\n                                    <p>Years are passed in as a pipe-delimited list of the four-digit year.</p>\r\n                                    <h4>Example</h4>\r\n                                    <p>http://life-measures.wdoitsolutions.com/api/index.php/us/scores/?key=yourRegistrationKey&amp;years=2003|2004|2005</p>\r\n                                    <div class="row">\r\n                                        <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns">\r\n                                            <div class="parameter-link">\r\n                                                <a href="#">Available U.S. Years\r\n                                                    <i class="fi-arrow-down"></i>\r\n                                                    <i class="fi-arrow-up"></i></a>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="parameter-list">\r\n                                                2001<br>\r\n                                                2002<br>\r\n                                                2003<br>\r\n                                                2004<br>\r\n                                                2005<br>\r\n                                                2006<br>\