	(297, 1, '2015-03-05 08:32:46', '2015-03-05 08:32:46', '<body id="data" class="page page-id-17 page-parent page-template-default win8.1 chrome chrome-0">\r\n<section class="intro-image" style="background-image: url(&#39;<?php echo TPATH ?>images/cki-template11-headers-getdata.jpg&#39;);">\r\n                <header>\r\n                    <h1>Download and Interact with the Project’s Data</h1>\r\n                    <hr>\r\n                </header>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <div id="content" class="row">\r\n                <a name="the-data-for-the-indices-of-well-being-are-available-in-four-different-sets-to-suit-different-research-needs"></a>\r\n                <section class="post box post-347 standard_post  large-6 medium-6 small-12 columns">\r\n                    <div class="border row clearfix">\r\n                        <header>\r\n                            <h2>The data for the Measures of Quality of Life are available in three different sets to suit different research needs.</h2>\r\n                        </header>\r\n                        <article>\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                <li>The Standard dataset interpolates missing scores between data points, but it does not back-fill or forward-fill missing values.</li>\r\n                                <li>The Chain-linked dataset uses chain-linking to create a series for overall Quality of Life and each of the dimensions appropriate for time-series analysis.</li>\r\n                                <li>The Raw dataset provides all input data used to create, with no alterations.</li>\r\n                            </ul>\r\n                            <p>In addition, the data can be downloaded through a REST-ful API, which allows for the creation of custom subsets of the Completed dataset.</p>\r\n                        </article>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </section>\r\n                                                \r\n                <a name="data-sets"></a>\r\n                <section class="post box data_sets large-6 medium-6 columns">\r\n                    <div class="border row clearfix">\r\n                        <div class="data_set clearfix">\r\n                            <header>\r\n                                <h2 id="us_data_sets">United States Data Sets</h2>\r\n                            </header>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Standard">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Standard</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexStandard.csv">CSV</a>\r\n                                        </span>\r\n                                    <span class="dta download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexStandard.dta">Stata</a>\r\n                                    </span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Chain-Linked">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Chain-Linked</span>\r\n                                    <span class="csv download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexChained.csv">CSV</a>\r\n                                    </span>\r\n                                    <span class="dta download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexChained.dta">Stata</a>\r\n                                    </span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Raw">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Raw</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexRaw.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                        <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>us_data/StateIndexRaw.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </article>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class="data_set clearfix">\r\n                            <header>\r\n                                <h2 id="world_data_sets">World Data Sets</h2>\r\n                            </header>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Standard">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Standard</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>world_data/WorldIndexStandard.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>world_data/WorldIndexStandard.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class="data_set_list Chain-Linked">\r\n                                    <span class="type">Chain-Linked</span>\r\n                                        <span class="csv download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>world_data/WorldIndexChained.csv">CSV</a></span>\r\n                                            <span class="dta download">\r\n                                            <a target="_blank" href="<?php echo TPATH ?>world_data/WorldIndexChained.dta">Stata</a></span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <